724431f-b.title: Manhattan: West End Avenue - 62nd Street (West)
724431f-b.text:
(1)
West End Ave., west side, north from West 62nd to 64th Streets. (Ave. not shown; it being on the extreme right. The view shows the excavation of buildings on this side, for the enlargement of the N.Y.C.R.R.
yards.
March 19, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, further northward. Building shown in the center, is on the S.W. corner of West 64th Street and West End Ave., and will also
be demolished.
March 19, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
724431f-b.folder: West End Avenue & 62nd Street (West), Manhattan, NY
